id382531491%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Midnight Menu-Tokimonsta']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/score.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/score.jpg" alt="Score / Matthew Herbert" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/score.php">Score<br />Matthew Herbert</a></h4><p>サントラが中心の心地よいジャズ演奏が心地よいアルバムです。昔を思い出などを回想しながらゆったりとお酒でも飲みたくなります。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000NDFJLE?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000NDFJLE" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Score-Matthew Herbert']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fscore%252Fid250308404%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Score-Matthew Herbert']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/selected.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/selected.jpg" alt="Selected / Nikakoi" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/selected.php">Selected<br />Nikakoi</a></h4><p>エレクトロニカ作品ですが、耳に痛いような内容ではなく、爽快なパッド音が心をリラックスさせてくれるような音楽です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B002TJBBIK?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B002TJBBIK" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Selected-Nikakoi']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%25